Замена: \(3^x=t,t>0\)
$$\frac{t+9}{t-9}+\frac{t-9}{t+9}-\frac{4\cdot 3\cdot t+144}{t^2-81}\geq 0\\ \frac{t+9}{t-9}+\frac{t-9}{t+9}-\frac{12t+144}{(t-9)(t+9)}\geq 0\\ \frac{(t+9)^2+(t-9)^2-12t-144}{(t-9)(t+9)}\geq 0\\ \frac{t^2+18t+81+t^2-18t+81-12t-144}{(t-9)(t+9)}\geq 0\\ \frac{2t^2-12t+18}{(t-9)(t+9)}\geq 0\\ \frac{t^2-6t+9}{(t-9)(t+9)}\geq 0\\ \frac{(t-3)^2}{(t-9)(t+9)}\geq 0$$
$$\displaystyle \left[ \begin{array}{l l}
t >9\\
t=3
\end{array} \right.$$
Обратная замена:
$$\displaystyle \begin{array}{{>{\displaystyle}l}}
\left[ \begin{array}{l l}
3^{x} >9\\
3^{x} =3
\end{array} \right.\\
\left[ \begin{array}{l l}
3^{x} >3^{2}\\
3^{x} =3^{1}
\end{array} \right.\\
\left[ \begin{array}{l l}
x >2\\
x=1
\end{array} \right.
\end{array}$$
Ответ: \(x\in (2;+\infty)~\cup\) {\(1\)}
